76
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:02,010
<font color="yellow">Jangan berpikir kasus ini sudah selesai.</font>

77
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:04,310
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak akan pernah menyerah.</font>

78
00:06:04,970 --> 00:06:07,140
<font color="yellow">Aku akan menyingkirkan semua penghalang yang kau buat.</font>

79
00:06:09,010 --> 00:06:10,240
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana?</font>

80
00:06:12,670 --> 00:06:14,440
<font color="yellow">Biar kuberi saran.</font>

81
00:06:22,610 --> 00:06:26,440
<font color="yellow">Orang-orang itu, tidak bisa kau lawan memakai hukum.</font>

82
00:06:28,910 --> 00:06:29,970
<font color="yellow">Kim Geomsa?</font>

83
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,440
<font color="yellow">Akhirnya kita bertemu.</font>

84
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,910
<font color="yellow">Aku Penyelidik Park Joon Pyo dari Badan Kehormatan Kejaksaan.</font>

85
00:06:38,110 --> 00:06:40,310
<font color="yellow">Kudengar seseorang meminta bantuanmu secara pribadi.</font>

86
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:42,710
<font color="yellow">- Apa kau bilang?
