92
00:07:05,510 --> 00:07:06,710
<font color="yellow">...adalah kau.</font>

93
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:19,610
<font color="yellow">Kim Geomsa sudah saya urus agar jangan sampai buka mulut.</font>

94
00:07:19,970 --> 00:07:21,310
<font color="yellow">Kerja bagus.</font>

95
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,840
<font color="yellow">Ibu anak itu... sebaiknya saya apakan?</font>

96
